reviewText: My daughter loves hip hop harry and the seller got us this movie very quickly. I'm not sure if there are anymore seasons, but if so I would love them.

My nephew(age 5) absolutely loves this video, and in a matter of days, had all the songs memorized. I love Hip Hop Harry because he's a great character for urban children to relate to and have a great time dancing to songs with out worrying about the content. I can't wait for the next video!

. . heard about Harry through a friend that heard about him through another friend, my 2 1/2 year old loves it; can't get him to stop watching it.  Only downfall is that I can't find any other copies in production besides the two that I bought.
Its hard to find Hip Hop Harry items - so this was a good buy. :)
